// HistoryDropdown
// Generic version-history dropdown used by DesignHistoryDropdown and
// DiagramHistoryDropdown. Displays a list of timestamped versions; selecting
// one loads that version's content for preview or revert.

FUNCTION HistoryDropdown(history, onVersionSelect, onClose) -> JSX     EXPORT
  Renders a scrollable list of version entries.
  Each entry shows a formatted timestamp.
  Clicking an entry calls onVersionSelect with that version object.
  Closes on click outside or Escape.
